title: Scrapheap Challenge - 11x06 - Giant Golf.avi
description:
"Dicks Diamonds" comprises regulars Dick Strawbridge and Jim Milner. Today's guest : Vin Poonwassie.

Their three challengers : "The Garage Widows", "The Broken Repairables" and "Dad's Heroes".

The challenge - build a golf playing machine.

Please help me seed & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

I'm adding one episode a day Mon - Fri as they air on ABC2 digital TV here in Australia. (We're getting them before the UK)
